# Configuration System Guide

The quiz application uses an embedded configuration system that allows customization without requiring a server.

## Configuration File

**[config-loader.js](mdc:config-loader.js)** contains the `EMBEDDED_CONFIG` object that controls:

- App branding (name, subtitle, organizer)
- UI text labels and buttons
- Round names and titles
- System messages (success, error, validation)
- Builder tool configurations

## Key Configuration Sections

### App Branding
```javascript
"app": {
  "name": "Mega Kvíz",
  "subtitle": "Otestujte své znalosti napříč různými tématy", 
  "title": "Mega Kvíz - Otestujte své znalosti",
  "organizer": "Martin Bil"
}
```

### UI Text Customization
All button labels, messages, and interface text can be customized through the `ui` section.

### Round Names
Customize quiz round names in `ui.rounds` array with fallback in `ui.roundFallback`.

## HTML Integration

Elements with `data-config` attributes automatically display configured text:
```html
<span data-config="ui.landing.topicSelection">Vyberte témata</span>
```

